The Kuber Industries 2x6 Feet Shaneel Bed Side Runner is a versatile and stylish addition to any home. Designed with a beautiful Rangoli print in multi-color, it adds a touch of vibrant elegance to your bedroom, living room, or kitchen.
This easy-to-clean runner is crafted from durable Shaneel fabric, ensuring longevity and comfort while maintaining its aesthetic appeal.
Whether placed beside your bed, in the kitchen, or as a decorative piece in your living room, this multipurpose runner offers both functionality and charm.
Its 2x6 feet size makes it the perfect fit for various spaces, offering protection for your floors and enhancing the decor effortlessly.,
- This bedside runner for bedroom adds a gentle surface underfoot, which helps in reducing floor impact while walking near the bed or other areas, offering ease to your daily routine., -
- Our machine washable runner keeps maintenance easy since it ensures you can clean stains or dust without any complicated cleaning processes, making it suitable for frequent use.,
- This runner for floor helps in safeguarding surfaces from scratches and stains because of its quality materials, which ensure reliability for various areas in your home.,
- This multipurpose bathroom runner fits perfectly in 2x6 feet spaces that suit kitchens, bedrooms, or living rooms, allowing versatile use in both small and large areas of your house.
